<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="34" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="34">• Robust, heavy-bodied marine mammals with external ear flaps, body furred except foreflippers, and hindflippers that rotate forward to enable walking; adult males 1-5-2 times longer and 3-6 times heavier than adult females.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
